<C>__{shifu }
<D>__{is something wrong?}
<A>__{reveal master oogway... a wise, old tortoise.}
<C>__{oogway}
<D>__{why must something be wrong for me to want to see my old friend?}
<C>__{shifu}
<D>__{so... nothing's wrong?}
<C>__{oogway}
<D>__{well, i didn't say that.}
<A>__{shifu looks up, concerned. oogway opens his mouth... and blows out a candle. and another candle. and another. finally, shifu uses his kung fu to blow them all out. oogway smiles knowingly.}
<C>__{shifu}
<D>__{you were saying?}
<C>__{oogway}
<D>__{i have had a vision... tai lung will return.}
