<C>__{zeng}
<D>__{yes, master shifu.}
<A>__{the goose flies off, but... smack! he hits a column. then he is off. back on oogway, as he walks toward camera, away from shifu.}
<C>__{oogway}
<D>__{one often meets his destiny on the road he takes to avoid it.}
<C>__{shifu}
<D>__{we have to do something. we can't just let him march on the valley, and take his revenge! he'll, he'll }
<A>__{oogway looks into the water of the moon pool.}
